            "id": "20260407A05LDL00",
            "title": "南华期货AB面：业绩双增获券商看好，内控失守频收监管罚单",
            "image": "https://inews.gtimg.com/om_ls/OK36ME_Y7vpUKET2BffjubWc7y9JuK81hlzKtoaa1OeTQAA_870492/0",
            "link": "https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260407A05LDL00",
            "author": "万众瞩目",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 16:50:11",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4月3日，浙江证监局对<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span class=\"qnt-link-text\">南华期货</span></span></span>及公司总经理贾晓龙分别出具警示函，指出公司存在采购内控制度执行失效、员工从业行为管理不到位等违规情形。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">警示函显示，经监管核查南华期货存在两项核心违规问题：一是采购等相关内控制度未得到有效落地执行并造成实际损失；二是对个别员工的从业行为管控不到位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice='1 1 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"p\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"margin-top: 24px;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"}]' style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">南华期货的行为违反了《期货公司监督管理办法》的相关规定，浙江证监局已要求南华期货在30日内提交书面整改报告，落实整改要求。</span></span></p><section style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6;margin-top:24px\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Oi3ZuyPa4a8V0c_J--o7tgITegbpoL8kEWvBZ-7fw93ckAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Oi3ZuyPa4a8V0c_J--o7tgITegbpoL8kEWvBZ-7fw93ckAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;visibility:visible;width:677px;height:100%\"/></section><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">与此同时，南华期货总经理贾晓龙因对上述违规行为负有直接管理责任，被浙江证监局一并出具警示函。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">值得注意的是，此次监管问责并非南华期货首次因内控合规问题 “踩线”，仅 2025 年一年内，公司就曾两次收到证监会系统的监管处罚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2025年9月，</span></span><span data-pm-slice='1 1 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"p\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"margin-top: 24px;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"}]' style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">南华期货沈阳营业部因微信群管理不规范、营销行为内控执行不到位，被辽宁证监局出具警示函，被要求</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">加强</span></span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">内控制度执行</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">，提升合规管理水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">同年11月，南华期货广东分公司因未妥善保存业务资料；未健全并有效执行有关业务管理、人员管理、投资者适当性等方面的管理与内控制度，被采取责令改正的行政监管措施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">而就在此次监管函下发前4天，南华期货披露了2025年度报告：营业总收入13.88亿元，同比增长2.45%；归母净利润4.86亿元，同比增长6.18%；扣非后归母净利润4.89亿元，同比增长7.67%，整体业绩平稳微增。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对比A</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">股其他两家上市期货公司，南华期货净利润不及</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">瑞达期货而优于</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">弘业期货。其中，</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">瑞达期货2025年营收和净利润分别为12.27亿元、5.47亿元；</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice='1 1 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"p\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\\"PingFang SC\\\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", \\\"Hiragino Sans GB\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei UI\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei\\\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\",\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\\"PingFang SC\\\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", \\\"Hiragino Sans GB\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei UI\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei\\\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\",\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"}]' style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">弘业期货</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2025年实现营业总收入2.87亿元，同比下滑20.53%；归母净利润399.27万元，同比大幅下降86.61%，净利润创出其A股上市以来新低。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">境外金融服务业务是南华期货2025年增长的核心引擎。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2025年，南华期货</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">期货经纪业务、</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">风险管理业务、</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">财富管理业务均出现不同程度下降，只有</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice='1 1 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"p\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"node\",{\"tagName\":\"span\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":null,\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"}]' style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">境外金融服务业务实现营收7.58亿元，同比增长15.79%，占总收入比重达55%。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">南华期货在年报中表示，国际化战略将依托境外子公司</span></span></span><span class=\"wx_search_keyword_wrap\" link-id=\"link-1775546808435-0.04752929752808832\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">横华国际</span></span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">为落脚点，遵循“深耕亚太、强化欧美、布局新兴”的总体思路，分阶段构建全球“多中心”网络。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">同时，南华期货还称，将逐步构建起“衍生品+财富+证券”的多维度国际业务体系，以期货衍生品能力赋能证券业务，证券与资管业务联动服务，打造独有竞争优势，实现由现阶段的衍生品交易与清算能力向综合金融服务能力的延伸，最后形成以</span></span><span class=\"wx_search_keyword_wrap\" link-id=\"link-1775546808435-0.2743087995198261\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">跨境衍生品</span></span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">为特色、多牌照协同服务中资出海的全链条金融供应商。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">年报发布后，多家券商机构点评看好，如兴业证券在研报中称，中长期看好南华期货依托稀缺性的牌照优势享受估值扩张：</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">一方面，2025年南华期货先后获得</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cboe clear</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">、</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nodal Clear</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">等清算所会员资格，作为国内唯一具备全球主流期货交易所清算牌照的期货公司，金融服务的国产替代逻辑有望推动保证金规模延续扩张。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">另一方面，</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2025</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">年公司完成港股上市，募资净额</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">12.03</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">亿港币将全部用于增资境外子公司横华国际，资本补充有望打开境外业务增长空间。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">业绩向好的背景下，南华期货的主要高管也普遍加薪。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">具体来看，董事长罗旭峰薪酬水平最高，2025年领取薪酬233.73万元，较2024年的198万元同比增长18.05%。本次警示函问责的总经理贾晓龙2025年薪酬为193.73万元，较2024年的165万元同比增长17.41%。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">此外，副总经理顾松、陈冬华的薪酬同比分别增长8.24%、11.08%，首席风险官李建萍的薪酬同比增幅则为12.87%。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">不过与高管普遍涨薪同时，南华期货人均薪酬却出现明显下滑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:24px\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.6\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2025年，南华期货薪酬总额4.28亿元，同比下降7.63%。期末员工总数1045人，同比仅减少0.67%。以期末人员计算，人均薪酬从44.4万元下降至41.3万元，降幅7.00%。</span></span></span></p><section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"margin-bottom:24px\"><section style=\"margin-top:24px\"><section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"margin-bottom:24px\"><section data-pm-slice='6 10 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"margin-top: 24px;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"data-role\":\"outer\",\"label\":\"edit by 135editor\",\"data-pm-slice\":\"0 0 []\",\"style\":\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"},\"namespaceU